#Read all the csv
df_PL_50 = pd.read_csv('Result_CSV/M_PL_50.csv', sep = ',', header=0) 
df_PL_EB = pd.read_csv('Result_CSV/PL_EB.csv', sep = ',', header=0)
df_PL_EC = pd.read_csv('Result_CSV/PL_EC.csv', sep = ',', header=0)
df_PL_ED = pd.read_csv('Result_CSV/PL_ED.csv', sep = ',', header=0)

In [3]:
#Comparison Mean degree=
plt.plot(df_PL_EB['meangrade'], df_PL_EB['Struc_Stab'], "b.",
         df_PL_50['meangrade'], df_PL_50['Struc_Stab'], "ro")
plt.xlabel('Mean Grade')
plt.ylabel('Structural Stability')
plt.title('M_PL_50 - PL_EB')
plt.grid(True)
plt.show()

#Spearman correlation M_PL_50
#SPearman correlation
spear_mean_20 = stats.spearmanr(df_PL_50['Struc_Stab'], df_PL_50['meangrade'])
spear_coop_20 = stats.spearmanr(df_PL_50['Struc_Stab'], df_PL_50['sum_coop'])
spear_comp_20 = stats.spearmanr(df_PL_50['Struc_Stab'], df_PL_50['sum_comp'])
spear_modu_eig_20 = stats.spearmanr(df_PL_50['Struc_Stab'], df_PL_50['Modularity_eig'])
spear_modu_opt_20 = stats.spearmanr(df_PL_50['Struc_Stab'], df_PL_50['Modularity_opt'])
spear_modu_greedy_20 = stats.spearmanr(df_PL_50['Struc_Stab'], df_PL_50['Modularity_greedy'])
